This is for following the tutorial at https://vulkan-tutorial.com

Using Ubuntu 22.04 LTS

Download the Google Shader Toolchain at https://github.com/google/shaderc/blob/main/downloads.md

sudo apt update 
sudo apt dist-upgrade 
sudo apt install vulkan-tools
sudo apt install libvulkan-dev
sudo apt install vulkan-validationlayers-dev spirv-tools
sudo apt install libvulkan-dev
sudo apt install libglfw3-dev
sudo apt install libglm-dev
sudo apt install make 
sudo apt install vim
sudo apt install build-essential 
sudo apt install libxxf86vm-dev libxi-dev


OR

sudo dnf install vulkan-tools
sudo dnf install vulkan-loader-devel
sudo dnf install mesa-vulkan-devel vulkan-validation-layers-devel
sudo dnf install glfw-devel
sudo dnf install glm-devel
sudo dnf install glslc
sudo dnf install g++

